mapper.select: SELECT * FROM rgdb."DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho" A WHERE A."logicalDeletedFlag" = FALSE AND A."shikibetsuCode" = #{識別コード} ORDER BY A."idoYMD" DESC, A."edaNo" DESC FETCH FIRST 1 ROWS ONLY

SELECT ,
FROM rgdb."DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho" AS "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki" AS "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki" ON "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."hihokenshaNo" = "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki"."hihokenshaNo" AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."taishoNendo" = "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki"."taishoNendo" AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."hokenshaNo" = "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki"."hokenshaNo" AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."seiriNo" = "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki"."seiriNo" AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."rirekiNo" = "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki"."rirekiNo" AND "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki"."isDeleted" = FALSE WHERE "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."taishoNendo" = #{対象年度} AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."hokenshaNo" = #{保険者番号} AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."seiriNo" = #{整理番号} AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."rirekiNo" = #{履歴番号} AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."isDeleted" = FALSE ORDER BY "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."hihokenshaNo" DESC, "DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki"."kanyurekiNo" ASC

WITH hihokenshaDaicho AS ( SELECT DbV1001."shikibetsuCode" FROM rgdb."DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho" as DbV1001 WHERE DbV1001."hihokenshaNo" = #{被保険者番号} AND DbV1001."logicalDeletedFlag" = FALSE ) SELECT
FROM hihokenshaDaicho LEFT OUTER JOIN
( SELECT ARRAY_AGG(CAST ("shikibetsuCode" AS TEXT)) FROM hihokenshaDaicho ) AS "ShikibetsuTaisho" ON hihokenshaDaicho."shikibetsuCode" = "ShikibetsuTaisho"."shikibetsuCode"

mapper.select: WITH T AS( SELECT A.* FROM rgdb."DbT3069KogakuGassanShinseishoKanyureki" AS A WHERE A."isDeleted" = FALSE AND A."taishoNendo" = #{対象年度} AND A."hokenshaNo" = #{保険者番号} AND A."seiriNo" = #{整理番号} ) SELECT M.* FROM T AS M WHERE M."rirekiNo" = ( SELECT MAX(N."rirekiNo") FROM T AS N WHERE M."taishoNendo" = N."taishoNendo" AND M."hokenshaNo" = N."hokenshaNo" AND M."seiriNo" = N."seiriNo") ORDER BY M."hihokenshaNo" DESC, M."kanyurekiNo" DESC
